and discovered that I was Kira.</i>

83
00:05:15,441 --> 00:05:16,484
<i>It couldn't be helped.</i>

84
00:05:17,151 --> 00:05:20,863
<i>There would be no other reason why
I would choose such an impulsive woman.</i>

85
00:05:21,989 --> 00:05:26,160
<i>Amane was doing Kira's killings.
But right now, it's me.</i>

86
00:05:27,620 --> 00:05:29,580
